column2: SELECT  GN.objID, GN.distance,s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.zErr, s.class, s.zWarning, s.snMedian,zp.z as zp, zp.zErr as zpErr, pht.modelMag_g, pht.modelMag_r, pht.modelMag_i, zp.absMagG, zp.absMagR, zp.absMagI, stf.logmass as starforming_logmass, p.logmass as passive_logmass, pca.mstellar_median as pca_logmass  FROM SpecObjAll as s  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#, #) AS GN ON s.bestObjID = GN.objID   JOIN Photoz as zp ON zp.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN PhotoObjAll as pht ON pht.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN stellarMassStarformingPort AS stf ON stf.specobjid = s.specobjid  JOIN stellarMassPassivePort AS p ON p.specobjid = s.specobjid  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscM1# AS pca ON p.specobjid = pca.specobjid WHERE  s.class = &&& AND   s.zWarning=# AND  s.z <=# AND  s.scienceprimary = # ORDER BY distance
